<topic>
<title>XSLT Rules</title>

<p>The basic rules in an XSLT stylesheet match elements in the
document and apply templates to those matches:</p>

<code>
&lt;!-- template applied to &lt;p> elements in the topic -->
&lt;xsl:template match="topic/p">
  &lt;p>
   &lt;xsl:value-of select="."/>
  &lt;/p>
&lt;/xsl:template>

&lt;!-- template applied to &lt;code> elements in the topic -->
&lt;xsl:template match="topic/code">
  &lt;pre>
   &lt;xsl:value-of select="."/>
  &lt;/pre>
&lt;/xsl:template>
</code>

</topic>

